title: Threads of Fate (PSX ISO) - 1999 Squaresoft Game
description:
This is an ISO I made myself earlier, because this happened to be one of ym favorite games on the PSX, and I was suprised at the lack of results in finding it in ISO form on the internet. So I did it myself, and decided I might as well share it.

Action/Adventure Game.

Wikipedia that shit for more info: http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Threads_of_Fate

I suggest running it with ePSXe and Delta 2.

Have fun.
